snippet.textDisplay:
I think the fact that it's sung by our childhood singer Shazia Manzoor G, who was like literally a face of Pakistani music. And now she comes back, and makes a song on how life goes on, turri jaandi ae, it really hits you hard, to see your childhood singer age, and you realize that you've probably aged yourself, and you're no longer a child in your parent's lap. 
Dil waleyan ne peeche mur vekhna bhi hai, kithe ture se, kithe aa chaliyee
